  "title": "Relationship Manager (Corporate Bank)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>*Seeking for a Relationship Manager/Junior Relationship Manager who has experience in handling Corporate Bank clients*</strong></em></p><p><strong>THE COMPANY</strong></p><p>This bank has a proven track record and is very stable. With their strong leadership and growth plans, they are currently seeking for a newly role created, Corporate Relationship Manager to be part of their Front office team.</p><p><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><ul><li>Be part of a team in RM work (Front office sales)</li><li>Grow/Hunt for existing clients network</li><li>Introduce new client accounts</li><li>Service the client</li><li>Sell the bank’s products</li><li>Perform hands-on credit risk writing, review and financial analysis</li><li>Ensure KYC/periodic KYC monitoring and documentation are complete</li><li>Collaborate effectively with other internal and external stakeholders</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Business/Finance/Economics/Accountancy/Commerce or any other relevant education</li><li>Minimum of 5 years as a Corporate Banking Relationship Manager </li><li>Independent, motivated, positive mindset, resourceful, strong interpersonal and communication skills</li></ul><p>If you will like to explore this opportunity, please email your resume in Microsoft Word format to marie@resolutehunter.com</p><p>We thank you for your interest and will contact shortlisted candidates for more detailed discussion.</p><p>For more job openings, please visit our website at https://resolutehunter.com/opportunities/</p><p>EA Licence 18C9105</p><p>EA Reg R1105305</p>",
